reviewText: Loved it - I received 2 cds, 1 dvd and a booklet. After just listening to part of one cd I felt blessed. The cds are great to listen to while commuting to school or work. It made me feel good this morning when someone told me "You have such a good attitude in the morning, I like you" I replied "Joel makes me feel Blessed and Highly Favored" Joel Osteen, in my ipod and car cd, makes me smile all day long.
